<!--
# Hello World - Entities as Functions

`beet_action` lets an entity behave like a callable function. `<Greet>` carries
a `name` field; `{RunOnLoad}` runs the entity's action once on load, which reads
the name and prints the greeting, then exits.

    beet --main=examples/action/hello_world.bsx
-->
<Greet{name:"world"} {RunOnLoad}/>
